title: Converse Wall to Wall - Boston
description:
Legendary Cambridge-based street artist Caleb Neelon brought his wealth of talents to Boston for the newest Wall to Wall installation. With spring colors as the palette, Caleb's pointillism-inspired piece on Brighton Ave in the heart of Allston brought a splash of color to the International Bicycle Centre.

To learn more about the Wall to Wall series visit:
http://www.converse.com/walltowall
